{"id": "1410874564505763891", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "872070639551414332", "author_name": "mc67", "author_bot": false, "content": "ハーメルンってどう使うんすかね？強い組み合わせとかあったら教えて欲しいです", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T06:31:48.960000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1410890046071902300", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "大体のキーカードを2回発動させるし追憶回旋曲は実質1コスト2ドローなんでデッキの圧縮になりますね", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T07:33:20.053000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1410897480148717639", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 19, "author_id": "512499694346305536", "author_name": "eyu17", "author_bot": false, "content": "基本的には狂気爆発、覚醒、追憶回旋曲が強いと覚えておけば良いと思います", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T08:02:52.475000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1410874564505763891", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1410897566253453403", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "512499694346305536", "author_name": "eyu17", "author_bot": false, "content": "ループ楽音や上行音など指令カードを2回発動させる効果が単純に強力なキャラで、現在はタヴィと組むことが多いです", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T08:03:13.004000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1410897626198704148", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "512499694346305536", "author_name": "eyu17", "author_bot": false, "content": "とはいえ指令カードを経由してスケールするキャラであれば誰でも相性はいいです（例として血鎖ヒロのチェインボールやケイケスの破れた沈戟など）", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T08:03:27.296000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1410898038066511966", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "512499694346305536", "author_name": "eyu17", "author_bot": false, "content": "狂気供給能力はないので主に狂気爆発でスケールするキャラが主体の構成では採用しにくいかもしれません。", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T08:05:05.493000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1410898584521408624", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "512499694346305536", "author_name": "eyu17", "author_bot": false, "content": "ドロー・コスト軽減・銀鍵充電・力スタックと多くの汎用的な役割をこなせるので、混沌を使う場合はとりあえず採用することも多いです。", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T08:07:15.778000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
